description: Redevelopment for mixed use purposes to provide 371 residential dwellings (1,2&3 bed units) 9,548 sqm of commerical uses in class B1 and/or D1, offices, studio workshops, cultural/dance space theatre, shop/food and drink (A1/A2/A3/A4/A5), gym/health fitness, new open space, landscaping, underground car parking (337) spaces, highway alterations, pedestrian & cycle routes.
